# Team Phoenix — EEG Prediction Error Pipeline

> A clean, milestone-organized EEG processing pipeline for studying prediction error signals in a VR reach-to-object task.

---

## Overview

This repository contains the full EEG analysis pipeline, milestone outputs, reports, and helper scripts for Team Phoenix's final project. The study investigates **prediction error signals** in EEG during a VR task, comparing brain responses to expected versus mismatched haptic feedback.

**Reference publication:**
Gehrke et al., CHI 2019 — *Detecting Visuo-Haptic Mismatches in Virtual Reality using Prediction Error Negativity of Event-Related Brain Potentials*
[DOI: 10.1145/3290605.3300657](https://doi.org/10.1145/3290605.3300657)

---

## ⚠️ Important: Shared / Review Version

This is a **filtered repository** prepared for instructor review. Large raw dataset folders are excluded to keep the repo lightweight and shareable.

